I'm very dubious about this.  When an uber guild is trying for CT their goal is to clear the complete zone as quickly as possible.  If I remember correctly CT will summon any mobs in the zone to his assistance so clearing it is vital (and if my memory is playing tricks on me, forgive the error).  Which means that an uber guild will pull as much as they can and AE kill it as quickly as they can, they don't want this to be an all day raid.  If done correctly CT will only be a few hours, from full zone spawn to completely empty.<br>
